<h2>Welcome to OpenRoles, <%= @user.first_name %>!</h2>

<p>Your OpenRoles account has been created successfully! For security reasons, we've set a temporary password that you must change before accessing your account.</p>

<div class="verification-code">
  <p>Your temporary password is:</p>
  <strong><%= @default_password %></strong>
</div>

<div class="verification-code">
  <p>Your password reset code is:</p>
  <strong><%= @verification_code.code %></strong>
</div>

<p><strong>Important:</strong> You cannot log in with the temporary password. You must set a new password first.</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" class="btn">Set Your Password</a>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info">
  <strong>Security tip:</strong> This password reset link will expire in 24 hours. If you didn't create an OpenRoles account, you can safely ignore this email.
</div>

<p>After setting your new password, you'll be able to log in and start exploring job opportunities!</p>

<p>Welcome aboard!<br>
The OpenRoles Team</p>
